==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undersphere
<hw>Un"der*sphere`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
sphere which is smaller than, and in its movements subject to, another;
a satellite.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An inferior sphere, or field of action.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underspore</ent>⟦br⟧
